text: Edgar Mulder (; born 22 November 1961) is a Dutch politician. He has been a member of the House of Representatives representing the Party for Freedom since 23 March 2017 and a member of the States of Overijssel since March 2011."E. (Edgar) Mulder" (in Dutch), Parlement & Politiek. Retrieved 15 April 2017. Mulder and his family live in Zwolle."Edgar Mulder " (in Dutch), Party for Freedom Overijssel.
